of women and children, and this is an indictment on our society,” she said . “This calls for greater action from all sectors to... put an end to this problem. 
For how long are we going to have to gather like this to speak on the same issue? How long till we see real action against
perpetrators of this injustice?” To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
